<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiin ka ngak gam lopi chu,
 Hung naiin Lal Immanuel;
 Ka lautha chung thangvan sangah,
 Nunnuom in leng tana.

[V2]
 Aw nang ka lenna gam lungmawl,
 Na tang chungah gimthei chate alang avai;
 Aw nang gam lopi lalna pak hawihin a bawm ie,
 Nang mai na hi ie, ka ngaih gam ninnuom.

[V3]
 2. Ka lautha leng lei gimum ah,
 Pak bangin chul tadih mahleh;
 Nawpna gam thiengtho tun tieng leh,
 Tuoi ni umta puona.

[V4]
 3. Simlei nunnuom lo banga chul,
 Hun muol liemsa ngaih a na ie;
 Nuoi simlei ah muonna umlo,
 Gimthei nau bang ka kap.

[V5]
 4. Isu, chawnban in ei kaiin,
 Na hehpih tuipi lien lut kau,
 Zion khuo nuom leh gam thiengtho,
 Muh ka nuom hi Lalpa.</lyrics>
<title>I Ngak Gam Lopi</title>
<author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>234</hymn_number>
</song>